title: Prospects Rising in the Draft & DJ's Mock Draft 3.0
itunes:title: Prospects Rising in the Draft & DJ's Mock Draft 3.0
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys discuss the challenges of the draft being fully virtual (1:32). Next, the trio look at which current prospects are rising during the draft process (8:21). After that, Rhett gives names of players who were risers and reaches in the past draft classes (14:53). To wrap up the show, Rhett and Bucky react to DJ's most recent mock draft (23:45).
